Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Why the pollsters got it wrong
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043w54r
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 16 Nov 1980
Humiliation for pollsters who made completely wrong call on the presidential election. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less